+------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                  Standard Schematization                          |
+------------------------------------------------------------------+
                                 |
                                 v
+------------------------------------------------------------+
|                      Sent Transaction                        |
|   (With Fee and Awaiting Confirmation from Miners)          |
+------------------------------------------------------------+
                                 |
                                 v
+------------------------------------------------------------+
|             Timeout for Unconfirmed Transaction              |
|   (e.g., 72 hours without confirmation)                     |
+------------------------------------------------------------+
                                 |
                                 v
+------------------------------------------------------------+
|          Automatic Detection of Unconfirmed Transactions     |
|                  and User Identification                    |
+------------------------------------------------------------+
                                 |
                                 v
+------------------------------------------------------------+
|           User Interface for Refund Request                  |
+------------------------------------------------------------+
                                 |
                                 v
+------------------------------------------------------------+
|                  Refund Smart Contracts                      |
|    (Handling Requests and Storing Information)               |
+------------------------------------------------------------+
                                 |
                                 v
+------------------------------------------------------------+
|           Timeout for Refund Acceptance                       |
|    (Period in which Miners can accept requests)             |
+------------------------------------------------------------+
                                 |
                                 v
+------------------------------------------------------------+
|          Refund and Miner Involvement                        |
|    (Mining Refund Transactions and Inclusion in a Block)     |
+------------------------------------------------------------+
                                 |
                                 v
+------------------------------------------------------------+
|               Confirmation and End of Process               |
| (Notification to Users and Cancellation of Transactions)     |
+------------------------------------------------------------+
                                 |
                                 v
+------------------------------------------------------------+
|        Feedback, Monitoring, and Reporting                  |
|   (Receiving User Feedback and Making Updates)               |
+------------------------------------------------------------+
